Original visual material and sampled audio
------------------------------------------

The code-native chess-piece drawings, launcher icon vectors, supporting color
resources, and fictional opponent identities under android/app/src/main are
original project material and are covered by the Drawless Chess
GPL-3.0-or-later grant. The seven opponent portraits were generated specifically
for this project with OpenAI's image-generation tool and without third-party
reference imagery. Their full-resolution masters, final prompts, derivation
details, and hashes are retained under artwork/opponents; to the extent copyright
or related rights subsist in those outputs, they are included in the same grant.
Move, capture, and castling sounds are processed only from the CC0 chess contacts;
fireworks are processed only from the CC0 pyrotechnic recordings. Glass-crack and
reserved UI sounds also use identified MIT recordings. All ship as mono 48 kHz
Ogg/Vorbis resources. The third-party recordings retain their original licenses;
Drawless Chess modifications and catalog code are covered by the project grant to
the extent applicable. Design and audit details are in docs/AUDIO_PROVENANCE.md.

